title: Bunkercast V: Nick Foles to the Bears
itunes:title: Bunkercast V: Nick Foles to the Bears
description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler recap all of the latest news around the league. As free agency frenzy begins to slow down, many teams are still making moves. We go to the kicker club and also hit some 8 o'clock delight.
